description:
Keyboard Workshop offers Chick's insights into the art and technique of making music. In a clear and straightforward way he explains and demonstrates his approach to practicing, improvising and composing. 

John Patitucci: bass
Tom Brechtlein: drums 
Chick Corea: piano

1987, VHS format.

Songs featured: 
Mood indigo
Easy to love
Children's song #16
Goldberg variation #1
Long fall 
Yellow Nimbus.
